steps.name: the user launches the automationexercise site
the user clicks the home page option in the navbar
Verify that home page is visible successfully
the user clicks on the Signup / Login button
to Validate the New User Sign up message is visible
Validate that the email field in the signup only accepts correct format emails
Type in "name" and "email" on the Sign up Form
the user clicks on the Sign up button
to validate the ENTER ACCOUNT INFORMATION Message is visible
Fill the details for the registration form
Validate the account created message being visible
Validate the -Logged in as username- being visible
the user clicks on the button log out
Validate the Login to your account message is visible
Validate with incorrect data, that the login will not pass without correct email and password
Validate that the email field in the login page has to have format AtDomaindotcom
enter the email and password user before to log in
click on the Login button
validate that Logged in as username is visible
Click on the Delete account button
